Where's the other
boy that was here?

35:43.600 --> 35:45.431
(SIREN WAILING)

36:02.745 --> 36:06.033
Put your guns down now!
This place is surrounded.

36:07.916 --> 36:10.578
Hoyt, do as
your friend is doing.

36:14.590 --> 36:17.047
It only takes one
bullet to make our statement.

36:17.968 --> 36:19.879
