36:20.095 --> 36:21.551
The message will be heard.

36:23.766 --> 36:24.881
Ugh!

36:35.778 --> 36:37.439
(GASPING)

36:55.798 --> 36:58.414
(SIREN WAILING)

37:03.806 --> 37:04.966
Alec?

37:07.643 --> 37:11.135
They're done
talking to your mom.
