DILLON: He's in good hands.

37:57.234 --> 37:58.223
Why don't you let
me take you back

37:58.318 --> 37:59.694
to the precinct,
we'll get you debriefed.

38:00.529 --> 38:01.860
You okay?

38:03.157 --> 38:04.317
Yeah.

38:19.256 --> 38:21.087
He's out of surgery.

38:22.843 --> 38:27.007
Doctors say he
tolerated itwell,
whatever the hell that means.

